OL,7,FA university academic who was sacked
OL,8,Fafter making comments criticising
OL,9,FIsrael has successfully claimed at an
OL,10,Femployment tribunal that he
OL,11,Fexperienced discrimination based on
OL,12,Fhis anti-Zionist belief in a landmark
OL,13,Fruling.
OL,15,FProfessor David Miller was also found
OL,16,Fto have been unfairly and wrongfully
OL,17,Fdismissed by the University of Bristol
OL,18,Fin October 2021.
