OL,7,FA disciplinary hearing found the
OL,8,Flecturer, who had worked as a
OL,9,Fprofessor of political sociology, "did
OL,10,Fnot meet the standards of behaviour"
OL,11,Fexpected of university staff.
OL,13,FProf Miller launched employment
OL,14,Ftribunal proceedings claiming unfair
OL,15,Fdismissal, breach of contract and
OL,16,Fdiscrimination or victimisation on
OL,17,Fgrounds of religion or belief.
