OL,7,FAt the conclusion of proceedings, Prof
OL,8,FMiller successfully claimed
OL,9,Fdiscrimination "based on his
OL,10,Fphilosophical belief that Zionism is
OL,11,Finherently racist, imperialist, and
OL,12,Fcolonial, a protected characteristic
OL,13,Funder the Equality Act 2010", his
OL,14,Flegal representatives, Rahman Lowe,
OL,15,Fannounced on Monday.
OL,17,F"This judgment establishes for the
OL,18,Ffirst time ever that anti-Zionist
OL,19,Fbeliefs are protected in the
OL,20,Fworkplace," the firm said.
