OL,7,FProf Miller said he is "very proud" to
OL,8,Fhave established that anti-Zionist
OL,9,Fviews qualify as a protected belief.
OL,11,F"I am extremely pleased that the
OL,12,FTribunal has concluded that I was
OL,13,Funfairly and wrongfully dismissed by
OL,14,Fthe University of Bristol," he said.
OL,16,F"I am also very proud that we have
OL,17,Fmanaged to establish that anti-Zionist
OL,18,Fviews qualify as a protected belief
OL,19,Funder the UK Equality Act.
