OL,7,F"This was the most important reason
OL,8,Ffor taking the case and I hope it will
OL,9,Fbecome a touchstone precedent in all
OL,10,Fthe future battles that we face with
OL,11,Fthe racist and genocidal ideology of
OL,12,FZionism and the movement to which it
OL,13,Fis attached.
OL,15,F"The determination that I was sacked
OL,16,Ffor my anti-Zionist views is a huge
OL,17,Fvindication of my case all the way
OL,18,Fthrough this process.
