OL,7,F"The University of Bristol maintained
OL,8,Fthat I was sacked because Zionist
OL,9,Fstudents were offended by my various
OL,10,Fremarks, but it was plain from the
OL,11,Fevidence of its own witnesses that
OL,12,Fthis was untrue, and it was the anti-
OL,13,FZionist nature of my comments which
OL,14,Fwas the decisive factor."
OL,16,FZillur Rahman, who represented the
OL,17,Facademic at the tribunal, said his
OL,18,Fclient has been "vindicated".
