OL,7,FHe said: "This is a landmark case and
OL,8,Fmarks a pivotal moment in the history
OL,9,Fof our country for those who believe
OL,10,Fin upholding the rights of
OL,11,FPalestinians.
OL,13,F"The timing of this judgment will be
OL,14,Fwelcomed by many who at present are
OL,15,Ffacing persecution in their workplaces
OL,16,Ffor speaking out against the crimes of
OL,17,Fthe Israeli state, and the genocide
OL,18,Ftaking place in Gaza.
OL,20,F"I am delighted for our client, David,
OL,21,Fwho has been vindicated."
