OL,7,FThe lawyer said his client will be
OL,8,Fseeking "maximum compensation" for the
OL,9,Fimpact the events have had on his
OL,10,Fcareer.
OL,12,FProf Miller drew controversy during a
OL,13,Flecture at the university in 2019,
OL,14,Fwhen he said the Zionist movement was
OL,15,Fone of five pillars driving
OL,16,FIslamophobia in the UK, the tribunal
OL,17,Fheard.
