OL,8,Freceived a complaint from the
OL,9,FCommunity Security Trust charity,
OL,10,Fwhich said his lecture was a "false,
OL,11,Fvile... antisemitic slur".
OL,13,FAfter an investigation of the
OL,14,Fcomplaint, no further action was taken
OL,15,Fagainst Scottish-born Prof Miller.
