OL,7,FBut further complaints were made to
OL,8,Fthe university about him after he took
OL,9,Fpart in an event called "Building the
OL,10,Fcampaign for free speech" in February
OL,11,F2021, in which he spoke of being
OL,12,Fpublicly criticised for his views on
OL,13,FPalestine and Israel.
OL,15,FThis led to the launch of disciplinary
OL,16,Fproceedings that culminated in his
OL,17,Fdismissal in October 2021.
