OL,7,FThe University of Bristol said in a
OL,8,Fstatement that it acknowledges the
OL,9,Fjudgment of the tribunal but is
OL,10,F"disappointed with its findings".
OL,12,FThe statement continued: "After a full
OL,13,Finvestigation and careful
OL,14,Fdeliberation, the university concluded
OL,15,Fthat Dr Miller did not meet the
OL,16,Fstandards of behaviour we expect from
OL,17,Four staff in relation to comments he
OL,18,Fmade in February 2021 about students
OL,19,Fand student societies linked to the
OL,20,Funiversity.
