OL,7,F"As a result and considering our
OL,8,Fresponsibilities to our students and
OL,9,Fthe wider university community, his
OL,10,Femployment was terminated.
OL,12,F"We recognise that these matters have
OL,13,Fcaused deep concern for many, and that
OL,14,Fmembers of our community hold very
OL,15,Fdifferent views from one another.
OL,17,F"We would, therefore, encourage
OL,18,Feveryone to respond in a responsible
OL,19,Fand sensitive way in the current
OL,20,Fclimate."
